data.description: Investor's Delight! Double the Charm, Double the Value! Say hello to this well maintained multifamily home that has been in the same family since it was built. The first floor unit boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, a spacious eat-in kitchen, and an expansive living room. The second floor mirrors the first floor layout. Both units are adorned with gleaming hardwood floors, vinyl replacement windows, and offer central air. The exterior of the home offers crisp white vinyl siding, a level lot, and two separate driveways for privacy and convenience of each tenant. Close to local shopping with easy access to highways, this a perfect commuter location!
